{"tid":37234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議員轟南港島綫限3卡","createTime":"2016-12-13T08:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T12:56:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"000e2d032f088ed15d059552c0e0accaf2736c66","tid":37234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161213/19863776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161213%2F19863776&d=l%2FbITXkwWEdtLkD7TdFzrQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=bf2ee671\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161213%2F19863776&h=fd6f154f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161213/19863776</a><br />\n<br />\n議員轟南港島綫限3卡<br />\n<br />\n6,655<br />\n ■立會鐵路事宜小組5名成員昨參觀南港島綫，田北辰（中）質疑月台規劃有誤。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■立會鐵路事宜小組5名成員昨參觀南港島綫，田北辰（中）質疑月台規劃有誤。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會鐵路事宜小組5名成員昨日參觀將在本月28日通車的港鐵南港島綫，並試坐無人列車。小組主席田北辰預料南港島綫月底開通後，將令金鐘人流量大幅增加，早上繁忙時間現時要等4班車過海，將來或等5至6班車。田又質疑列車只限3卡，是將自己「封頂」，難以應付人潮。<br />\n田指現時政府規劃南港島綫的無人駕駛列車為3卡車，繁忙時間每小時最多載約14,000人，日後最多只能加至2分鐘1班車，即繁忙時間每小時載到21,000人。田批評現時月台設計無彈性增加車卡，擔心將來又要再開闢新隧道應付人潮，「你知政府啲規劃成日錯，又要起條新綫、掘條新隧道，我覺得係有問題，點解唔將個月台加大啲，預留多1至2卡車呢？而係將自己封頂」。<br />\n田又擔心無人駕駛列車沒有港鐵職員，如有意外發生，便無人教導乘客如何逃生。<br />\n■記者李詠希  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n70萬賬戶或納懶人基金<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n遊戲卡疑致敏　逾7,000張已流出"},{"pid":"b299f387cae50ecbb51cda608d551b74d8a89a5a","tid":37234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"起好晒先知 ?<br />\n<br />\n入計劃書嗰陣無人睇定無人理 ?"},{"pid":"0a052b6192c1941ef02ef196aabd4f35657de1ae","tid":37234,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起好晒先知 ?<br />\n<br />\n入計劃書嗰陣無人睇定無人理 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n田北俊細佬不意外"},{"pid":"3f50e72a23bfd31dbcd5bb88db3e59fecbd00556","tid":37234,"uid":8426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:51:18.000Z","msg":"田生既時間慢左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c651f21748c71ed0566d8b9a30a9676fe4a643b1","tid":37234,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"而家先屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8a46758dddb5c7ba5f3e739826874bc3f01c03","tid":37234,"uid":39141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"二少條廢柴, 唔係話自己好撚熟鐵路嘅咩!!!<br />\n好撚多線眼喺地鐵做咩?? <br />\n宜家先話唔知得3卡???<br />\n抵你一世活喺你大佬陰影下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cea0a17373bee0c2a5cd012b09086ed080c0ea4","tid":37234,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"895e7901b089b0c8334bcf7f482e2b17a6d476d5","tid":37234,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>田生既時間慢左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n田二少好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9d8cdf72c4daec45d3330a359e8dfb4215f46b","tid":37234,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:16:30.000Z","msg":"田北<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f020f66f5efab2d14fa0bc72ce8d47208c4d5319","tid":37234,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"學馬鐵加長月台囉"},{"pid":"ecd956432b24234ee5c33f008b4a2def7bb07a7d","tid":37234,"uid":33238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"見南區友嘈佢咪跟口水味嘈兩句囉"},{"pid":"71d8e05ff99c3d4872e81ab500ae4c178cfc9b9b","tid":37234,"uid":23769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201