re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"南港島線多客d金鐘咪塞得仲勁"},{"pid":"cc2f046e8f43cad1e8124e9e7010f1648da95c6a","tid":37234,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:08:17.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚我地啲港島人"},{"pid":"113d08b90c4754a7d61bf6a3b62ef586e0ad5ad6","tid":37234,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"等睇無人搭 香港仔隧道繼續塞到爆炸"},{"pid":"4744ba2f98fa4f609c261c295d8143ae37322d0c","tid":37234,"uid":7585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"住香港仔,田灣先仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜車都CUT哂,地鐵又唔到"},{"pid":"0beadada394ba7b87f9d4cd7d360df8a25d4ef80","tid":37234,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南港島線多客d金鐘咪塞得仲勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係一早唔應該連去金鐘"},{"pid":"90201b0350cc090d75dc4d82f6fe549019589d4d","tid":37234,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>南港島線多客d金鐘咪塞得仲勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係一早唔應該連去金鐘</blockquote><br />\n金鐘會塞一件事<br />\n佢封頂個月台只容納到3卡<br />\n以後解決左金鐘問題<br />\n佢都要起過晒南線設施先可以增加載客量先係問題<br />\n跟本就劃地自限<br />\n重蹈當年港島線唔起雙軌覆轍"},{"pid":"ffef5fac12a6c4394b5a8bfd943157ba5ef7e587","tid":37234,"uid":28905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>南港島線多客d金鐘咪塞得仲勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係一早唔應該連去金鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該照其中一個方案駁埋灣仔，灣仔負責去東區方向轉車咁樣分流"}]}